briefDescription: We are a non-profit social enterprise operating a network of self-sustainable, just-around-the-corner primary health centers that provide affordable and high quality primary and preventive healthcare services to the low income population.We currently operate a network of 18 primary health centers in Mumbai slums serving a total population of 1.5 million people. We have served over 500,000 patient encounters with a recovery rate of above 90% and satisfaction rating of above 90%.We are looking to expand to 52 centers across Mumbai  and expand to atleast 2 more cities in the next 3 years
